'''Abydos''' may mean:

*[[Abydos, Egypt]], an Ancient Egyptian city
*[[Abydos (Hellespont)]], an ancient city of Mysia, in Asia Minor
*[[Abydos (Stargate)|Abydos (''Stargate'')]], name of a fictional planet in the ''Stargate'' science fiction universe
*[[Abydos Station]], a pastoral lease and cattle station in Western Australia

'''Abidos''' may mean:
*[[Abidos, Pyrénées-Atlantiques]], a commune of the Pyrénées-Atlantiques ''département'', in southwestern France

'''Abidu''' may mean:
*[[Abidu]], a village in Iran
